Title: Studio Journal: Experimenting with Texture
Date: 2026-06-10
Source: mira_010_studio_journal.pdf
Demo Persona: Mira Vale
Privacy Level: private

Spent five hours painting. I experimented with a new heavy gel medium to add physical texture to the background. Some parts dried unevenly, but I learned how the material reacts to different drying temperatures. I'll adjust my technique on the next attempt.